Features two episodes of this news program, in the first one the show visits New York for a Leather and Lace show and ask New Yorkers about bare skin as it is not allowed there. The "news anchors" stand in front of the camera in what apper to be swin suits, read the news and along the way disrobe as they talk. An audition is included. A review of Fast Food Nation and Extras 01 are shared. Several gals appear of different skin tones, shaved and /or pierced. The second show is on a beach in Canada where the show appears to be made, it also includes reviews and a video game is evaluated. There is a cooking segment with the gal cooks wearing clear aprons. The talkers do seem to project their voices a bit loudly. Occasional swearing. An unforgetable experience.
this dvd was almost like an avertisement for Naked News. If this is what they call "Best of" well I realy would not like to see the rest of the volums.
